<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<em>A cape worn by a hero from <a class="nonexistent" href="./Valinor">Valinor</a>, a land utterly beyond the strife of elements.</em> <p>
The Cloak 'Colluin' [1, +20] is a relatively low level <a href="./artifact">artifact</a> that is quite good, but can be superseded by better cloaks relatively quickly. 
</p>
<p>
It can be activated for resistance (20+d20 turns) every 111 turns if it is being worn. This is good, as it already provides basic resists (see below). By being activated for resistance, you get stacking DOUBLE resistance, reducing your damage from an element to 1/9 (1/3 * 1/3) and providing ALMOST as good coverage as an immunity. 
</p>
<p>
It provides resistance to acid, electricity, fire, cold and poison. 
</p>
<p>
It allows you to sense the presence of good beings.  
</p>
<p>
It cannot be harmed by acid, cold, lightning or fire. 
</p>
